267
00:14:38,310 --> 00:14:41,040
Lupin, the guy from
that internet game?

268
00:14:41,040 --> 00:14:42,910
Quit acting like a hotshot
just ’cause you went viral!

269
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:44,880
[GRUNT]

270
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,180
You Bastard!

271
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:57,490
[GRUNTING]

272
00:14:57,490 --> 00:14:59,160
Is that all you--

273
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,300
You shouldn’t mess
with grown ups, boys.

274
00:15:02,430 --> 00:15:04,170
I’m Lupin III.

275
