trying, chump?

283
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:31,590
Huh?

284
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:34,000
Why did you come after me?

285
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:36,300
I should be asking the
questions, here, saying goodbye

286
00:15:36,300 --> 00:15:37,530
out of the blue like that.

287
00:15:37,530 --> 00:15:39,970
As promised, you stole me away.

288
00:15:39,970 --> 00:15:42,570
