290
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:46,780
There’s no reason for
us to stay together.

291
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:48,240
I happen to be
the type of person

292
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,140
who takes good care
of the things I steal.

293
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,150
That’s not true.

294
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:55,050
I saw the condition of
your loot at the villa.

295
00:15:55,050 --> 00:15:56,120
It didn’t look like you were
taking care of it at all.

296
00:15:58,090 --> 00:15:59,050
Well, yeah, you got me there.

297
00:16:01,290 --> 00:16:02,860
Why didn’t you just leave
me at the airport in France?

298
00:16:04,830 --> 00:16:07,030
Well, it just kind
of ended up that way.

299
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,700
Why do you let me
stay in your room?

300
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:10,700
I asked you to do a job for me.

301
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:11,570
There are other
hackers out there.

302
00:16:11,570 --> 00:16:14,970
[BUZZING]

303
00:16:14,970 --> 00:16:17,570
Given what’s happened
since we’ve met,

304
00:16:17,570 --> 00:16:21,110
I can only assume that you
just want me to accompany you.

305
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:23,080
Well, you know, deductive
reasoning like that

306
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:24,850
can only lead to theories.

307
00:16:24,850 --> 00:16:26,520
So I dug a little deeper.

308
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:28,380
Hm?

309
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:30,950
I’ve been implanted
with a tracking device.

310
00:16:30,950 --> 00:16:32,090
Really?

311
00:16:32,090 --> 00:16:33,690
Well, who did that to you?

312
00:16:33,690 --> 00:16:35,690
Someone who knew
my exact location

313
00:16:35,690 --> 00:16:37,290
and pursued me to
no end, you see.

314
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:40,730
And that’s why you
wanted to leave?

315
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:43,770
It was the most efficient
and logical thing to do.

316
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:49,370
Conclusion, Lupin
III is protecting me.

317
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:49,710
Answer.

