Flowers?

323
00:16:58,450 --> 00:16:59,180
It’s a Japanese saying.

324
00:17:00,450 --> 00:17:03,020
Yes, hello, underworld.

325
00:17:03,020 --> 00:17:05,090
You don’t have to look it up.

326
00:17:05,090 --> 00:17:07,560
What I’m trying to say is--

327
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:08,390
it’d be lame if I said it.

328
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:14,030
Do you want to have
sex with me, Lupin?

329
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:16,060
No!

330
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:18,000
Hm?

331
00:17:22,540 --> 00:17:24,340
You got the wrong idea.

332
00:17:24,340 --> 00:17:26,440
If I left you on
your own, can’t you

333
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:28,040
see that Marco Polo would
continue to chase you

334
00:17:28,040 --> 00:17:30,180
to the ends of the earth?

335
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:33,080
I just want to keep you
safe until things calm down.

336
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:34,150
Ah, just forget about it.

337
00:17:37,820 --> 00:17:38,690
I still don’t understand
what you mean.

338
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,360
To be honest, I don’t
either, anymore.

339
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:42,720
Hm?

340
00:17:51,970 --> 00:17:53,940
Speak of the devil himself.

341
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:56,640
Marco Polo have finally
made their move.

342
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,910
Bringing in hit men,
talk about low tech, huh?

343
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:05,480
His hotels and
restaurants, he even

344
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:08,420
posts when he’s taking
a bath and going to bed.

345
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:10,450
You’d be hard pressed to find
a target that makes it easier

346
00:18:10,450 --> 00:18:10,920
to track them down.

347
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:14,320
Let’s take that truck.

348
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:19,230
You’re... Shinpei Mayama?

349
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:25,870
Whoa!

350
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,370
I recognize you.

351
00:18:31,370 --> 00:18:32,770
Not your face, but your MO
