367
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:39,940
right?

368
00:19:44,850 --> 00:19:47,320
I think it’s rather convenient
that this website accepts

369
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:48,380
untraceable digital
currency, huh?

370
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:05,230
It’s a game totally
free of danger or risk

371
00:20:05,230 --> 00:20:07,340
on my end, Lupin III.

372
00:20:26,020 --> 00:20:26,960
Emmy, get back.

373
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:32,430
And don’t even think
